      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation or equivalent formal mesh convergence study with GCI computation required across all operating points.",
      "rationale": "A three-level mesh refinement study was performed at a single operating point. GCI was not computed at all five flow-speed combinations. Achieved level 2 does not satisfy the required level 4."
