    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors were evaluated against MRL 5 requirements. Seven factors were formally assessed; all seven achieved levels fall below required levels. Six factors were flagged as not assessed, representing epistemic gaps that cannot be resolved with current evidence. The overall credibility package does not meet the minimum threshold for a Class III VAD submission at Model Risk Level 5. The decision outcome is Not accepted pending resolution of all identified gaps.",
